        "listicle_item_RtCU4x": {
          "type": "listicle-item",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/dark_circles.png",
            "image_aspect_ratio": "1_1",
            "title": "1. Feels so luxurious you won't believe it's science-backed therapy",
            "content": "<p>Meet the most indulgent and effective eye treatment ever created. Imagine being able to <strong>enjoy the most relaxing, spa-like experience while actually reversing years of under-eye aging.</strong> The Eye Glow Kit's red light therapy glasses feel like a luxurious retreat, but they're powered by clinically-proven technology that <strong>stimulates collagen production, reduces inflammation, and restores youthful radiance.</strong> Say goodbye to harsh chemicals, painful procedures, and disappointing results. </p>",
            "highlight_text": "",
            "enable_container": false
          }
        },
        "listicle_item_zDcz3V": {
          "type": "listicle-item",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/before_after_1.png",
            "image_aspect_ratio": "1_1",
            "title": "2. You can ditch expensive spa treatments and become your own aesthetician",
            "content": "<p>Skip the $200+ spa appointments, long waiting lists, and inconsistent results. The Eye Glow Kit makes it so easy to create <strong>professional-grade results right from your bedroom.</strong> Within minutes you can achieve what dermatologists charge hundreds for, and do it in the comfort of your own space. Stop overpaying with your time and money at expensive clinics and start becoming your own skincare expert — it's relaxing, effective, affordable, and scientifically proven!</p>",
            "highlight_text": "",
            "enable_container": false
          }
        },
        "listicle_item_gfdexG": {
          "type": "listicle-item",
          "settings": {
            "image_aspect_ratio": "1_1",
            "title": "3. As simple or advanced as you want your routine to be",
            "content": "<p>With <strong>multiple treatment modes and customizable session lengths,</strong> you can create the perfect routine for your lifestyle. Want a quick 5-minute morning boost? Done. Prefer a luxurious 15-minute evening ritual? Perfect. Whether you're a skincare minimalist or a beauty enthusiast, you can officially personalize your under-eye care your way with the Eye Glow Kit!</p>",
            "highlight_text": "multiple treatment modes and customizable session lengths",
            "enable_container": false
          }
        },
        "listicle_item_4Jy6iC": {
          "type": "listicle-item",
          "settings": {
            "image_aspect_ratio": "1_1",
            "title": "4. It's the ultimate money-saver compared to professional treatments",
            "content": "<p>By using the Eye Glow Kit to recreate professional red light therapy at home, you'll save thousands that you would typically spend on dermatologist visits, spa treatments, and injectable procedures. <strong>One single botox session costs more than this entire device!</strong> You will never want to spend $300+ on under-eye treatments again after experiencing Eye Glow Kit results.</p><p><strong>BONUS:</strong> You can get the Eye Glow Kit for just $79.99 (60% off) with FREE premium serum for a limited time here.</p>",
            "highlight_text": "One single botox session costs more than this entire device!",
            "enable_container": false
          }
        },
        "listicle_item_kzXURm": {
          "type": "listicle-item",
          "settings": {
            "image_aspect_ratio": "1_1",
            "title": "5. You can finally ditch harsh chemicals and invasive procedures",
            "content": "<p>Traditional under-eye treatments often involve <strong>harsh retinoids, chemical peels, or painful injections</strong> that can cause irritation, downtime, and unpredictable results. Red light therapy is completely natural, non-invasive, and works with your body's own healing processes. The Eye Glow Kit harnesses the power of clinically-proven wavelengths to naturally stimulate collagen production and cellular repair without any side effects.</p><p><strong>Scientific Fact:</strong> Red light therapy at 660nm has been shown to increase collagen synthesis by up to 31% in clinical studies!</p>",
            "highlight_text": "harsh retinoids, chemical peels, or painful injections",
            "enable_container": false
          }
        },
        "listicle_item_FFLGth": {
          "type": "listicle-item",
          "settings": {
            "image_aspect_ratio": "1_1",
            "title": "6. It's the trending beauty secret celebrities won't stop talking about",
            "content": "<p><strong><em>Editor's Note: A-list celebrities are obsessed with red light therapy! 🌟</em></strong> From Hollywood stars to beauty influencers, everyone is discovering the anti-aging power of targeted red light therapy. Social media is buzzing with before-and-after transformations, and the Eye Glow Kit is leading the revolution in at-home professional treatments. Join the millions who've discovered this cutting-edge technology that's reshaping the beauty industry!</p>",
            "highlight_text": "A-list celebrities are obsessed with red light therapy!",
            "enable_container": false
          }
        },
        "listicle_item_DDUedz": {
          "type": "listicle-item",
          "settings": {
            "image_aspect_ratio": "1_1",
            "title": "7. Avoid the afternoon energy crash that tired eyes create",
            "content": "<p>When your under-eyes look tired, puffy, and aged, it affects your entire appearance and confidence. <strong>The visible signs of fatigue can make you feel older and less energetic</strong> throughout the day. The Eye Glow Kit's red light therapy provides a natural \"awakening\" effect, reducing puffiness, brightening dark circles, and creating that well-rested, youthful glow that makes you look and feel more vibrant all day long.</p>",
            "highlight_text": "The visible signs of fatigue can make you feel older and less energetic",
            "enable_container": false
          }
        },
        "listicle_item_rfABjG": {
          "type": "listicle-item",
          "settings": {
            "image_aspect_ratio": "1_1",
            "title": "8. It makes your entire skincare routine more effective",
            "content": "<p><em><strong>Pro Tip: Use the Eye Glow Kit before applying your favorite eye creams for maximum absorption! 💡</strong></em> The red light therapy increases circulation and prepares your skin to better absorb nutrients from your skincare products. Many users report that their expensive eye creams work significantly better when combined with Eye Glow Kit treatments. It's like having a professional aesthetician prep your skin for optimal product penetration every single time!</p>",
            "highlight_text": "Use the Eye Glow Kit before applying your favorite eye creams for maximum absorption!",
            "enable_container": false
          }
        },
        "listicle_item_LBygwj": {
          "type": "listicle-item",
          "settings": {
            "image_aspect_ratio": "1_1",
            "title": "9. There have been over 100,000+ treatments completed with SereneLift technology",
            "content": "<p>The Eye Glow Kit has helped thousands of customers achieve dramatic under-eye transformations with <strong>over 210 five-star reviews and counting!</strong> With proven results showing visible improvements in just 30 days, our customers are obsessed with how easy and effective red light therapy can be. From busy professionals to beauty enthusiasts, people of all ages are discovering the life-changing benefits of at-home red light therapy.</p>",
            "highlight_text": "over 210 five-star reviews and counting!",
            "enable_container": false
          }
        },
